snippet.title: MOM MURDERED & MAJOR IS MISSING! ACTIVE AMBER ALERT!
snippet.description:
There is an active Amber Alert for a missing 3-year-old boy named Major P. Harris. He was last seen on October 14,2021 on 37th and Clark. His mother, Mallery Muenzenberger was found murdered. The "person of interest" in her homicide Jaheim Clark was the last one seen with little Major. Jaheim was tracked down and as law enforcement surrounded the house they heard two shots. Jaheim shot himself and we still don't know where Major Harris is. The Amber Alert was also for Jaheim's vehicle:
2008 Black Chevy Equinox LIC #ABE 2804 
Here is the link to the live: 
https://www.facebook.com/watch/live/?ref=search&v=281875883790163

If you see Major Harris call 911. 
If you have tips on the case call (414) 935-7405 
Thanks for watching & please consider subscribing!
